Package fws_master

Class Summary
Binding Binding is the abstract base class for binding parameters to stations.
ConfigParameter A ConfigParameter is a Parameter that will be submitted to the slave.
FWSMaster This is the main class of this program.
InputParameter A input parameter is transfered from the slave to the master an represents a type of collected data.
MasterContentHandler Loads the general configuration parameters of the master.
Measurement A Measurement is a value received of a slave.
MeasurementCollector A thread that pulls the data of the stations.
MeasurementHistory A History of Measurements.
MeasurementHistoryController This class handles the collection of HistoryValues.
MeasurementHistoryEntry A Timestamp + Value.
ModBusWrapper This class wraps the jaMod library.
Parameter A Parameter is the base class for any kind of values that are sent to slaves or received by the master.
ParameterContentHandler Load all parameters from the xml config file
ParameterController This class handles a list of Parameters.
PersistencePreferences Class for loading configuration file.
PlotBase Abstract base class for plots
PlotConfig A PlotConfig is created for each plot that a user configures for a input binding.
PlotController List of all Classes that implement the PlotBase
PlotTime Plot with x axis as time stamps and y axis the values of the measurements
Station A Station represents a slave.
StationConfigBinding This class represents a Binding of a ConfigParameter to a Station.
StationContentHandler Loads the Stations from the configuration files.
StationController Manages a List of all Stations
StationInputBinding Allows binding a InputParameter to a Station.
